<view class="page album-engage">
  <block wx:if="{{status === 'loading'}}">
    <view class="page-content album-engage__pad">
      <ui-skeleton rows="{{4}}" title="{{true}}" />
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:elif="{{status === 'error'}}">
    <view class="page-content">
      <ui-empty title="无法打开" description="{{errorMessage}}" actionText="返回" bind:action="onBack" />
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="page-content album-engage__body">
      <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}">
        <text class="album-engage__section-title text-h3">关于本次服务</text>
        <text class="text-body">{{albumTitle}}</text>
      </ui-card>

      <text class="text-caption text-secondary album-engage__hint">
        服务与记录评价在完工后填写；配件核对可随时进行；问题反馈用于反映具体疑问。
      </text>

      <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}" class="album-engage__option" bindtap="onOpenReview">
        <view class="album-engage__option-head">
          <text class="text-h3">服务与记录评价</text>
          <ui-tag wx:if="{{hasReview}}" variant="success" text="已评价" />
          <ui-tag wx:elif="{{!eligible}}" variant="info" text="完工后可评" />
        </view>
        <text class="text-caption text-secondary">
          维修服务与相册记录分开评分，可选授权展示在公开案例。
        </text>
      </ui-card>

      <ui-card
        wx:if="{{hasParts}}"
        shadow="{{true}}"
        padding="{{true}}"
        class="album-engage__option"
        bindtap="onOpenPartVerify"
      >
        <view class="album-engage__option-head">
          <text class="text-h3">核对配件</text>
          <ui-tag variant="info" text="可随时填写" />
        </view>
        <text class="text-caption text-secondary">
          核对相册登记的更换配件是否与实物一致，与评价无关。
        </text>
        <text wx:if="{{partVerifySummary}}" class="text-caption album-engage__sub">{{partVerifySummary}}</text>
      </ui-card>

      <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}" class="album-engage__option" bindtap="onOpenFeedback">
        <view class="album-engage__option-head">
          <text class="text-h3">问题反馈</text>
        </view>
        <text class="text-caption text-secondary">
          图片看不清、节点缺失、车辆信息有误等具体问题。
        </text>
      </ui-card>
    </view>

    <ui-login-sheet
      visible="{{loginSheetVisible}}"
      mode="auto"
      bindContext="album"
      bind:close="closeLoginSheet"
      bind:cancel="closeLoginSheet"
      bind:success="onLoginSuccess"
    />
  </block>
</view>
